ved error name `DMLERR_BUSY`, proving the field-value lookup ran.\n\n- `tests/src/net.java.dev.jna/jna-platform/5.3.1/src/test/resources/META-INF/native-image/reachability-metadata.json`\n  - Added Native Image metadata for the Ddeml public fields and proxy needed by the refined test path.\n  - Added the JNA `libjnidispatch` resource for this test class.\n\n- `metadata/net.java.dev.jna/jna-platform/5.3.1/reachability-metadata.json`\n  - Updated Ddeml metadata to expose all public fields for `DdemlException`.\n  - Added supporting Ddeml proxy and JNA native resource metadata needed for the successful initialization path.\n\nPer instruction, I did not compile or run tests.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0bbb39c135ee2d310169f985870b48819694478ad451987e05\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 983, "output": 1356, "cacheRead": 71168, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 73507, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777960311728, "responseId": "resp_0bbb39c135ee2d310169f985789bd4819680f00246bce4c17f"}, "toolResults": []}
